{"type":"message","id":"66d549e0","parentId":"74084e5d","timestamp":"2026-04-02T05:44:37.285Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session found is the cron job session itself (the one running right now). There are no other active user conversations in the last 5 minutes. The cron job session is just checking itself, not a user conversation.\n\nSo I should proceed with autonomous learning - searching for industry news about enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services.\n\nLet me search for the latest news in these areas.","thinkingSignature":"f85d9aeeff019976a58f973c0c162c4e2cd846b05dc6ac2a42fd87858acd5cf4"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到只有当前cron任务会话，没有用户活跃对话。执行自主学习。\n"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":874,"output":162,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45017,"cost":{"input":0.0002622,"output":0.00019439999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017760299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775108670447}}
